metadata.name: Lady Death
metadata.description:
**Mesmerising Lady Death**

Have you ever wondered about the Death? Who is she? In what guise does she come? What happens when you look into her eyes? What do you see in them? Fear, yourself or maybe your sins? 

Lady Death in all her terrifying beauty looks at you.
